  "selection": "Top ~500 series by BLS popularity rank per survey, with OE and WM bumped to 2,000 because they're point-in-time surveys with one observation per series. JOLTS (JT) ships a 20-series hardcoded fallback because it isn't covered by the catalog or popular_series APIs. Total: ~10,500 series across 28 surveys.",
